{"tid":1929247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿: 反對中共散布不實消息, 將新型肺炎責任轉嫁美國","createTime":"2020-03-16T23:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T07:36:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a061d66b6195e8c18e7a5b2ac879eab915ed0382","tid":1929247,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:36:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國國務卿蓬佩奧(Secretary Pompeo) : 中共頻道不斷散播不實消息</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1239610871585951744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1239610871585951744&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8L%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=388a8001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1239610871585951744&h=87342e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1239610871585951744</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/qZ6oezO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZ6oezO.jpg&h=05f5249d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514885-20200317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514885-20200317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8L%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=0aeeaf02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514885-20200317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=73c5cb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514885-20200317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中央政治局委員、中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪，應約與美國國務卿蓬佩奧通電話。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國國務院發言人歐塔加斯發表聲明，表示蓬佩奧向楊潔篪表達美方強烈反對中國試圖將新型肺炎病毒疫情的過錯，轉嫁到美國，又指現時不是散布虛假信息和離奇謠言的時候。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，楊潔篪表示，中國的新型肺炎疫情防控形勢持續向好，批評美國一些政客，不斷詆毀中國和中方防控努力，對中國進行污名化，激起中國人民強烈憤慨，中方對此堅決反對，予以強烈譴責。美方應該立即糾正錯誤，停止對中國的無端指責。中方正告美方，任何詆毀抹黑中國的圖謀都不可能得逞，任何損害中國利益的行為都必將遭到中方的堅決反擊。新華社的報道，未有交代蓬佩奧的回應。"},{"pid":"7fb938026adcdd5c19919552823e797d63ec50fa","tid":1929247,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ffb2471662260aab8be9c32350d2998a7dcf0","tid":1929247,"uid":120458,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:37:38.000Z","msg":"口交部：我反對你個反對"},{"pid":"8735e26f7059fd2bd8cc2b94522d56732d1820e3","tid":1929247,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:48:22.000Z","msg":"跳過領事 口交部，一搵就搵楊潔篪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下中共保唔保亮劍班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25827358795f815eed06c8d92136087098874629","tid":1929247,"uid":45255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8735e26f7059fd2bd8cc2b94522d56732d1820e3","tid":1929247,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:48:22.000Z","msg":"跳過領事 口交部，一搵就搵楊潔篪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下中共保唔保亮劍班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:50:37.000Z","msg":"白宮揸弗人使同你口交部對口？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b8e4a46e7fd4931c0fc751bc4b39de5b6cc407","tid":1929247,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"支共一定會收聲，同中国制造 2025 一樣"},{"pid":"644febf12b20583a74e36244b6c9f998ed0fbab7","tid":1929247,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />響應美國，反攻大陸"},{"pid":"655f4bfcfe266a7cfbc3ad4431673719ef32750f","tid":1929247,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"twitter戰線要人"},{"pid":"2cf73ff4b828524